'''September 26''' is the 26th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  and its day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1568|ja|1568|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  entered the capital on behalf of {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
